<p>爱心接力！我想握紧妈妈的手！去战胜疾病！</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/images01/20200822/050760ed34aa4e0c8d63deaf09dd3f64.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/images01/20200822/7ec64e273d874d4995a14bcd81b39171.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20200822/79cc5016128847de9d40e5d2fcabffc2.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/images01/20200822/abb8d4e848874c6a855db451b94d52b8.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>            <div class="lookall-box">
